BASE URL FOR PRODUCTION BUILD: https://zn23g4uvg2.execute-api.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/prod

VALIDATIONS:
	Password must be 8 characters or more

To create a new recipe:
  POST /recipes
	JSON:
		name: string
		imageUrl: string
		description: string
		category: string
		ingredients: []string
		instructions: []string
		preparationTime: int
		isPublic: bool
		difficulty: string

To get all recipes:
	GET /recipes?category={category you want to filter by (OPTIONAL)}
	To get next batch:
		GET /recipes?last={last key returned}&category={category you want to filter by (OPTIONAL)}

To edit a recipe (NOT YET WORKING):
	PUT /recipes/{recipe_id}
	JSON:
		name: string
		imageUrl: string
		description: string
		category: string
		ingredients: []string
		instructions: []string
		preparationTime: int
		isPublic: bool
		difficulty: string

To delete a recipe:
	DELETE /recipes/{recipe_id}

To add recipe to favorite:
	POST /favorites
	JSON:
		recipeId: string

To remove recipe from favorite:
	DELETE /favorites/{recipe_id}
	
To get all favorites recipes (NOT YET WORKING):
	GET /favorites
	To get next batch:
		GET /favorites?last={id of last favorite returned}

To rate a recipe (NOT YET WORKING):
	POST /ratings
	JSON:
		recipeId: string
		stars: int
		comment: string

To delete rating on a recipe (NOT YET WORKING):
	DELETE /ratings/{id of recipe}

To get all ratings on a recipe (NOT YET WORKING):
	GET /ratings/{id of recipe}
	To get next batch:
		GET /ratings/{id of recipe}?last={last key returned}

To get url to post pictures to:
	GET /upload-url